
- The fonts must be copied into the folder
  '/home/openerp/current/git_repositories/PCAP1/pc_generics/fonts/ocrbb.ttf'
  in order to generate the makos with the appropriate fonts.
  Make the path readable.

- Font ocrbb.ttf was copied from module l10n_ch_payment_slip in v7:
  https://github.com/OCA/l10n-switzerland/tree/7.0/l10n_ch_payment_slip/report
